<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Sepracor started.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Sepracor started.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-07-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Gruntal &amp; Co said it had initated coverage of Sepracor Inc with a strong buy rating.</p>
<p>-- said set a one-year price target of $37, based on a potential EPS breakout of $5.00 per share in 2001.</p>
<p>-- said expects company to file a New Drug Application for four additional new products by 2001, including improved versions of top-selling brands Hismanal, Foradil/Serevent, Proventil/Ventolin and Ditropan.</p>
<p>-- Sepracor was up 1/4 to 25-1/8.</p>
